Package: cdmAcm0010
Title: Implementation of CDM Large-Scale Methodology ACM0010
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Christiaan", family = "Pauw", email = "christiaan.pauw@gmal.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides tidyverse-aligned tooling to operationalise the Clean Development Mechanism methodology ACM0010 "Consolidated methodology for emission reductions from manure management systems". The package exposes applicability checks, equation-level helpers, monitoring-period aggregation, simulation utilities, and a meta-estimator that reproduces greenhouse gas accounting for anaerobic digestion projects treating organic wastewater and manure streams.
